<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="dig-v">dig <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪɡ/    美 /dɪɡ/  </p>
<p>(dug, dug)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>掘 (土)；挖 (洞、沟 等)；采掘：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>dig for</strong> gold / dig a hole
掘金/挖洞</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="dig-into">dig (...) into</h3>
<p>1.<strong>插入；戳进；探究：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She dug into her purse and took out some coins.
她从钱包里掏出一些硬币。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We both focused on digging into the characters we were going to play.
我们俩都集中精力钻研要饰演的角色。</p><footer>2017 全国改</footer></div>

<h3 id="dig-out">dig out</h3>
<p>1.<strong>挖出；找出；发现：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The army organized teams to dig out those who were trapped and to bury the dead.
军人组成小分队，挖出被困者，掩埋遇难者。</p><footer>人教① – 4</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The truth was dug out.
真相被发现了。</p></div>

<h3 id="dig-up">dig up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>掘起；开垦 (荒地)；搜集：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Cutting down trees and digging up grass can cause deserts and sandstorms to increase.
砍树挖草能导致沙漠变大、沙尘暴增加。</p><footer>外研③ – 4</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>People in many places are digging up the old folk stories.  
许多地区的人都在搜集古老的民间故事。</p></div></div>